com.swfm.mica
Interface MiiModelIOFormatManager

All Superinterfaces:
MiiModelEntity, MiiModelTypes
All Known Implementing Classes:
MiModelIndentedTreeIOFormatManager, MiModelIOFormatManager, MiModelIOXMLSax2FormatManager
public interface MiiModelIOFormatManager
extends MiiModelEntity

This is the interface for classes that support the reading and writing of MiiModelDocuments from and to Streams. The format of data in the stream is totally up to the implementer of this interface. See the MiModelInputOutput class for a sample implementation.
